VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT HostnameVerifier\s*\{\s*.*true\s*\}|TrustAllCerts|setHostnameVerifier\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:test|development|localhost|staging
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects TLS certificate/hostname verification bypass patterns.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Ktor Insecure Trust Manager / TLS Bypass.
